stateDiagram-v2
  [*] --> Idle
  Idle --> Load
  Load --> Ready: data accepted
  Load --> Idle: rejected
  Ready --> Homing: reference required
  Homing --> Ready: complete
  Ready --> MoveXY: start
  MoveXY --> Dosing: arrived
  Dosing --> Advance: action complete
  Advance --> MoveXY: next point
  Advance --> Complete: last point
  MoveXY --> Fault: stop/timeout
  Dosing --> Fault: stop/timeout
  Complete --> Idle: reset
  Fault --> Idle: authorised reset
